我是一个刚刚开始学习编mod的小渣渣，所以请不要乱喷情况如题
（我只是编程的时候发现一直报错，然后直接把1.8.9的教程复制过来还是报错，所以我想应该是版本问题）
因为我找不到1.12.2的mod开发教程，所以只能请教一下

mod主类代码：

报错在第28行“GameRegistry.register(myBlock);”   “register”处报错
package net.hakugyokurou.diracon;

import net.hakugyokurou.diracon.item.MyBlock;
import net.minecraft.block.material.Material;
import net.minecraft.creativetab.CreativeTabs;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.Mod;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.Mod.EventHandler;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.event.FMLInitializationEvent;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.event.FMLPostInitializationEvent;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.event.FMLPreInitializationEvent;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.registry.GameRegistry;

@Mod(modid="diracon", name="Diracon", version="1.0.0")
public class Diracon {
        public static MyBlock myBlock;
        
        
        
        @EventHandler
        public void preLoad(FMLPreInitializationEvent event)
        {
                final String myModId = "diracon";
                final String myBlockId = "myblock";
                myBlock = new MyBlock(Material.ROCK);
                myBlock.setUnlocalizedName(myModId + "." + myBlockId);
                myBlock.setRegistryName(myModId, myBlockId);
                myBlock.setCreativeTab(CreativeTabs.BUILDING_BLOCKS);
                GameRegistry.register(myBlock);
        }
         
        
        
        
        @EventHandler
        public void load(FMLInitializationEvent event)
        {
        }
         
        
        
        
        @EventHandler
        public void postLoad(FMLPostInitializationEvent event)
        {
        }
}


报错信息：
Bound mismatch: The generic method register(K) of type GameRegistry is not applicable for the arguments (MyBlock). The inferred type MyBlock is not a valid substitute for the bounded parameter <K extends IForgeRegistryEntry<K>>



MyBlock.java

